{"tid":45660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子中刀嗌救命 倒卧沙田坳道血泊中","createTime":"2016-12-19T06:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-19T06:32:10.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"142d6c3bf1cd98673b81a1a62125f396c51d2f64","tid":45660,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161219/56066144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161219%2F56066144&d=3KeJokIXu7Kwz9DZ1CRXU0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=f7117392\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20161219%2F56066144&h=b3bd99e1\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20161219/56066144</a><br />\n<br />\n雲山沙田坳邨對開的沙田坳道，中午12時12分，一名男子駕駛黑色保時捷四驅車到埗，停泊路邊後落車準備步行上山。突然手機響起，他甫接聽，即撲出兩名持刀大漢從後施襲。事主手、背部及小腿中多刀，其中小腿傷口血流如注，他受傷倒地，兇徒逞兇後即跳上自備私家車逃去。據報，傷者曾經大叫救命，當時數名休班懲教署職員路經，見狀後協助替傷者急救，事主稍後送往伊利沙伯醫院救治，據悉，事主為商人。<br />\n<br />\n約半小時後，警方在竹園的獅子山郊野公園附近，發現一輛被燒毀的凌志私家車，不排除是兇徒棄車放火，毀屍滅迹，現正封鎖調查。"},{"pid":"7d714287b9de89a91b20683d0e74e890c1883f20","tid":45660,"uid":12021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:28:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b7070835ccec97c6747c432d14e4e2c1ed411ee","tid":45660,"uid":39800,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-19T06:32:10.000Z","msg":"痴線<br />\n日光日白都斬人"}]}